title: BRIEF-ARMS Medical And Tissue Regenix BioSurgery Sign Exclusive Distributor Agreement
text: February 26, 2018 / 4:13 PM / Updated 5 minutes ago BRIEF-ARMS Medical And Tissue Regenix BioSurgery Sign Exclusive Distributor Agreement Reuters Staff 1 Min Read Feb 26 (Reuters) - Tissue Regenix Group Plc: * ARMS MEDICAL AND TISSUE REGENIX BIOSURGERY SIGN EXCLUSIVE DISTRIBUTOR AGREEMENT FOR DERMAPURE® ALLOGRAFT WITH DCELL® TECHNOLOGY * ‍ARMS MEDICAL SAYS DEAL GIVES CO EXCLUSIVE RIGHTS TO DISTRIBUTE TISSUE REGENIX BIOLOGIC THROUGHOUT U.S. FOR USE IN UROLOGY & GYNECOLOGY PROCEDURES​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
